Great composition by Noori with hardrock and heavy metal pieces.  Has some similarities  when Metallica did an awesome concert with San Francisco symphony ( Metallica S & M album).

People who don't like this song ,do not have the taste in rock/metal music which is fine but please don't downgrade this great attempt.
